*Special Resolution #728 from California State Senator Wadid P. Deddeh, (September 18, 1991);& Special Resolution #1729 from California State Senator Denise Moreno Ducheny (December 8, 2006).<ref name="Prodigal Son, Child of The King" />
*Special Resolution from CA State Senator Denise Moreno Ducheny (December 8, 2006) resolution number 1729.<ref name="Prodigal Son, Child of The King" />
*Letter of Commendation from US Congresswoman Shelia Jackson Lee, (November 8, 2005).<ref name="Prodigal Son, Child of The King" />
*Commission as Colonel on staff of New Mexico, State Governor Bill Richardson (December 19, 2005).<ref name="Prodigal Son, Child of The King" />
*Special Proclamation from Houston, Texas, Major  Lee Brown (April 7, 2001).<ref name="Prodigal Son, Child of The King" />
*"Goodwill Ambassador" Commission by Arkansas State Governors Jim Guy Tucker (November 6, 1993) & Mike Huckabee (September 18, 1998).<ref name="Prodigal Son, Child of The King" />
*Special Proclamation from El Paso, Texas, Major  Larry Francis (January 26, 1996).<ref name="Prodigal Son, Child of The King" />
*Executive Order Proclaiming Oct 6th 1996 "Benjamin O. Jimerson Day" in the City of Albuquerque, NM, Mayor Martin J. Chavez.<ref name="Prodigal Son, Child of The King" />
*Executive Order 05-169, from Albuquerque NM, City Mayor Martin J. Chavez.<ref name="Prodigal Son, Child of The King" />

